Functional Requirements
The system shall allow users to register and log in.
The system shall allow students to add assignments.
The system shall allow students to edit assignments.
The system shall allow students to delete assignments.
The system shall display all assignments in a dashboard.
The system shall allow users to set deadlines.
The system shall send reminders before deadlines.

Acceptance Criteria: Notifications must be sent at least 24 hours before deadline.

The system shall allow users to mark assignments as completed.
The system shall categorize assignments by subject/module.
The system shall allow users to search assignments.

Acceptance Criteria: Search results must display within 2 seconds

Non-Functional Requirements
Usability
The system shall have a simple and intuitive interface.
The system shall be accessible on mobile and desktop.
Deployability
The system shall be deployable on cloud platforms.
The system shall support modern web browsers.
Maintainability
The system shall include clear documentation.
The code shall follow modular design principles.
Scalability
The system shall support up to 1000 users.
The system shall handle increased data efficiently.
Security
User data shall be encrypted.
The system shall require authentication.
Performance
The system shall load pages within 2 seconds.
Notifications shall be sent in real-time or near real-time.
